room_title: Escape room "The Moonlight Gallery" by Escape Room Downtown in Canton
room_description: An elderly eccentric Malin from Canton owns a private gallery studio. Rumor has it that Malin hid his most prized gemstones within it, leaving clues for his heirs to find them. But the crime syndicate your gang is associated with has found out about Malin's secret. The mob has created a diversion, having cut the power to the building and its alarm system. You have only 45 minutes to find the jewels and get out before you're discovered by the night watchman!
